cat << EOF
GemRB (Game engine made with preRendered Background) is a portable open-source
implementation of Bioware's Infinity Engine which was written to support
pseudo-3D role playing games based on the Dungeons & Dragons ruleset. It
should run on GNU/Linux, Microsoft Windows, OS X and possibly other UNIX
derivatives. It licensed under the GPL.
